-      <p permid="RLW">
+      <p>
         The integers mod <m>n</m> have become indispensable in the theory and applications of algebra.
         In mathematics they are used in cryptography, coding theory,
         and the detection of errors in identification codes.
       </p>
 
-      <p permid="xTf">
+      <p>
